And as far as the 'loot 'n agro distribution' part of this thread goes, since we don't have a Warrior main in guild who plays regularly, ALL of our good armor (and weapon if appropriate) loot currently goes to our highest SK if it's an upgrade for her, even if she is not present when the item drops in the case of tradeables, as she is our main tank at the present time.  It just makes sense, if she is going to hold agro for us that we invest in her, erm, infrastructure as it were... (and a fetching infrastructure it is too <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   ).  We've had no complaints re item distribution as of yet, fortunately when you are small it is easy for people to understand the 'pull for the team' mentality... We do try to take care of everyone, and choose raid locations based on how we can help the greatest number of people with quests, upgrades, etc.<br>
